abstracts.cdata!:
The project would be carried out over a
            three-year period and consists of: (a) about 18 man-years of
            planning experts for establishing a long-range development
            plan and a detailed investment program, and (b) about 25
            man-years of internationally recruited experts for
            strengthening LEC's management and for training
            LEC's staff.
